{
  "stem": "14190.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Soon after they-- their march, they took over our city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All sorts of proclamations were announced.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, Jews were-- Jewish kids were not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to-- to-- to do a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, my father was still working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's why I think that he probably tampered with papers and wanted to-- to come as Aryan.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were supposed to wear yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember very well how my mom was making those and putting on me and on my sister.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were not allowed to walk on the sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to-- we had to walk where the gutter is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Not allowed to go to schools, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My sisters stayed home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were all sorts of-- it was a campaign to humiliate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was campaign to degrade, and to humiliate, to belittle, and to demean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Very soon afterwards, I can't tell you the dates, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's so difficult for me, even this is-- you need to look up for-- it's well-documented.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it shouldn't be very difficult to find the exact dates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember very well march to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were allowed to take only the things that we can carry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Unfortunately, or fortunately, we did not march with the first group to ghetto because I think my father was managed-- managed to tamper our census, with our papers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "However, it didn't take very long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they did find out that we are Jews and there were other people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we were gathered in a special place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from there, we were marching.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so we were the last people, the last group, that were marching to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
